<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NodeNotes — Think in connections</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicons/favicon.ico">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicons/favicon-16x16.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicons/favicon-32x32.png">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/favicons/apple-touch-icon.png">

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #111;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        }

        /* ---------- Navbar ---------- */
        .navbar-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px 20px 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            background: #fff;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .nav-box {
            background-color: #000;
            border: 2px solid #000;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1040px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .nav-brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.3px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .nav-actions { display: flex; gap: 10px; }

        .btn-light-bordered {
            background: #000;
            color: #fff;
            border: 2px solid #fff;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 6px 18px;
            transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
        }
        .btn-light-bordered:hover { background: #fff; color: #000; }

        .btn-fill-white {
            background: #fff;
            color: #000;
            border: 2px solid #fff;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 6px 18px;
            transition: opacity 0.15s;
        }
        .btn-fill-white:hover { opacity: 0.82; color: #000; }

        /* ---------- Hero ---------- */
        .hero {
            max-width: 1040px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 70px 20px 40px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 50px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.05;
            letter-spacing: -1.5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .hero .lead {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            color: #444;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            max-width: 480px;
        }

        .hero-ctas { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; }

        .btn-dark-cta {
            background: #000;
            color: #fff;
            border: 2px solid #000;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
        }
        .btn-dark-cta:hover { background: #fff; color: #000; }

        .btn-ghost-cta {
            color: #000;
            border: 2px solid #000;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            background: #fff;
            transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
        }
        .btn-ghost-cta:hover { background: #000; color: #fff; }

        .hero-note {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #888;
            margin-top: 16px;
        }

        /* ---------- Graph preview ---------- */
        .graph-preview {
            border: 2px solid #000;
            border-radius: 6px;
            background:
                linear-gradient(#0000000a 1px, transparent 1px) 0 0 / 22px 22px,
                linear-gradient(90deg, #0000000a 1px, transparent 1px) 0 0 / 22px 22px,
                #fff;
            box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 #00000010;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .graph-preview svg { display: block; width: 100%; height: auto; }

        /* ---------- Sections ---------- */
        .section {
            max-width: 1040px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 50px 20px;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.8px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .section-sub {
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }

        .feature-card {
            border: 2px solid #000;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 26px 24px;
            height: 100%;
            background: #fff;
            transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
        }
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 #00000012;
        }
        .feature-icon {
            width: 46px;
            height: 46px;
            border: 2px solid #000;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .feature-card h5 { font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .feature-card p { color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 0; line-height: 1.55; }

        .feature-card.accent-yellow .feature-icon { background: #fffde7; border-color: #f9d000; }
        .feature-card.accent-green  .feature-icon { background: #e8f5e9; border-color: #43a047; }
        .feature-card.accent-blue   .feature-icon { background: #e3f2fd; border-color: #1e88e5; }
        .feature-card.accent-dark   .feature-icon { background: #000; }

        /* ---------- How it works ---------- */
        .steps { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
        .step-num {
            width: 38px; height: 38px;
            background: #000; color: #fff;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 14px;
        }
        .step h6 { font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
        .step p { color: #555; font-size: 0.93rem; margin: 0; }

        /* ---------- Final CTA ---------- */
        .cta-band {
            background: #000;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 6px;
            max-width: 1040px;
            margin: 30px auto 0;
            padding: 50px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cta-band h2 { font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.6px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .cta-band p { color: #cfcfcf; margin-bottom: 26px; }

        /* ---------- Footer ---------- */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #999;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            padding: 40px 20px 30px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 860px) {
            .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding-top: 40px; }
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.3rem; }
            .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <div class="navbar-wrapper">
        <nav class="nav-box">
            <a href="/" class="nav-brand">
                <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <rect x="8" y="4" width="24" height="32" rx="2" fill="#fff" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2"/>
                    <rect x="8" y="4" width="6" height="32" rx="2" fill="#bbb" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2"/>
                    <line x1="18" y1="13" x2="28" y2="13" stroke="#000" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                    <line x1="18" y1="19" x2="28" y2="19" stroke="#000" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                    <line x1="18" y1="25" x2="28" y2="25" stroke="#000" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                </svg>
                NodeNotes
            </a>
            <div class="nav-actions">
                <a href="/login" class="btn btn-light-bordered">Log In</a>
                <a href="/register" class="btn btn-fill-white">Sign Up</a>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <header class="hero">
        <div>
            <h1>Your notes,<br>finally connected.</h1>
            <p class="lead">
                NodeNotes turns scattered ideas into a visual map. Drop a node for every
                thought, write a note inside it, and draw the connections that link them —
                all on an infinite canvas that saves as you go.
            </p>
            <div class="hero-ctas">
                <a href="/register" class="btn btn-dark-cta">Create your free account</a>
                <a href="/login" class="btn btn-ghost-cta">I already have one</a>
            </div>
            <p class="hero-note">No credit card. Sign up with email or your Google account.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Visual concept preview -->
        <div class="graph-preview">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 460 360" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <!-- edges -->
                <g stroke="#000" stroke-width="2">
                    <line x1="140" y1="90" x2="300" y2="70"/>
                    <line x1="140" y1="90" x2="120" y2="250"/>
                    <line x1="300" y1="70" x2="340" y2="220"/>
                    <line x1="120" y1="250" x2="340" y2="220"/>
                    <line x1="120" y1="250" x2="250" y2="300"/>
                </g>
                <!-- nodes -->
                <g>
                    <rect x="80"  y="60"  width="120" height="60" rx="6" fill="#fffde7" stroke="#f9d000" stroke-width="2"/>
                    <text x="140" y="86"  text-anchor="middle" font-family="Segoe UI" font-size="14" font-weight="700" fill="#333">Project idea</text>
                    <text x="140" y="104" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Segoe UI" font-size="11" fill="#777">start here</text>

                    <rect x="248" y="44"  width="104" height="52" rx="6" fill="#e8f5e9" stroke="#43a047" stroke-width="2"/>
                    <text x="300" y="74"  text-anchor="middle" font-family="Segoe UI" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="#333">Research</text>

                    <rect x="66"  y="222" width="108" height="56" rx="6" fill="#e3f2fd" stroke="#1e88e5" stroke-width="2"/>
                    <text x="120" y="254" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Segoe UI" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="#333">Tasks</text>

                    <rect x="288" y="194" width="104" height="52" rx="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#000" stroke-width="2"/>
                    <text x="340" y="224" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Segoe UI" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="#333">Notes</text>

                    <rect x="198" y="276" width="104" height="50" rx="6" fill="#fffde7" stroke="#f9d000" stroke-width="2"/>
                    <text x="250" y="305" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Segoe UI" font-size="13" font-weight="700" fill="#333">Done ✓</text>
                </g>
            </svg>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Features -->
    <section class="section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Built for the way you actually think</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">Ideas aren't lists — they branch, link and loop. NodeNotes lets them.</p>

        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <div class="feature-card accent-yellow">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#000" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="18" r="3"/><line x1="8.5" y1="8.5" x2="15.5" y2="15.5"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h5>Visual canvas</h5>
                    <p>Pan, zoom and arrange your nodes freely on an infinite board.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <div class="feature-card accent-green">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#000" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 18l6-6-6-6"/><line x1="3" y1="12" x2="15" y2="12"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h5>Connect ideas</h5>
                    <p>Draw links between nodes to map how your thoughts relate.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <div class="feature-card accent-blue">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#000" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z"/><path d="M12 12V4"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h5>Color by priority</h5>
                    <p>Tag nodes with colors so what matters most stands out instantly.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <div class="feature-card accent-dark">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h5>Private &amp; saved</h5>
                    <p>Your boards are tied to your account and saved automatically.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How it works -->
    <section class="section" style="padding-top: 10px;">
        <h2 class="section-title">Three steps to your first map</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">From blank canvas to connected thinking in under a minute.</p>
        <div class="steps">
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-num">1</div>
                <h6>Create a board</h6>
                <p>Sign up and open a fresh, infinite canvas for any topic.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-num">2</div>
                <h6>Add nodes &amp; notes</h6>
                <p>Drop nodes anywhere and write the details inside each one.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step-num">3</div>
                <h6>Connect the dots</h6>
                <p>Link related nodes and watch the structure of your idea appear.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <section class="cta-band">
        <h2>Start mapping your ideas today</h2>
        <p>It's free to begin. Create an account and open your first board in seconds.</p>
        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-fill-white" style="padding: 12px 32px; font-size: 1rem;">Create your free account</a>
    </section>

    <footer>
        © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> NodeNotes · Think in connections.
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
